yew Windsor chairs beside an Eileen Gray glass and chrome table. In the
background is Eileens Gray's Lota Sofa (Omitted). Photograph Zeev Aram in
the Heath Street shop with an 18th century Germany oak bureau and Shiro
Kuramata's chest of drawers (Omitted).
